</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Higashiyama" /><category term="Gardens" /><category term="Foliage" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Red leaves illuminated by the sun, over the pond in the villa's expansive garden. 太陽に照らされた紅葉、別荘の広い庭の池の上。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2511_A7R00894_x.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2511_A7R00894_x.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Arashiyama Afternoon ・午後の嵐山</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/251120/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Arashiyama Afternoon ・午後の嵐山" /><published>2025-11-20T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2025-11-20T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/arashiyama</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/251120/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
