</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Katsura River" /><category term="Boats" /><category term="Foliage" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[People out on boats in Arashiyama's Oigawa river, enjoying the colored foliage on the mountains above. 嵐山の大堰川でボートを楽しみながら、山々の紅葉を眺める人々。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2511_A7R00876_x-2.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2511_A7R00876_x-2.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Kamigamo Shrine・上賀茂神社</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/251119/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Kamigamo Shrine・上賀茂神社" /><published>2025-11-19T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2025-11-19T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/kamigamo-jinja</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/251119/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
