私はここに来て峡谷を縫うように流れる大堰川を見下ろすのが大好きだ。

ここからたくさんの写真を撮ってきた。</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Katsura River" /><category term="Foliage" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[I love coming up here and looking down at the Katsura/Oi/Hozu River (it changes names) as it winds its way through the gorge. I've taken many photos from here.]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2511_A7R00665_x.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2025/2511_A7R00665_x.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry></feed>